text: Bacharuddin Jusuf Habibie (25 June 1936 - 11 September 2019) was an Indonesian engineer who was President of Indonesia from May 21, 1998 to October 20, 1999. ==References== ==Related pages== *List of scientists *List of Asian scientists by country Category:Indonesian Muslims Category:Presidents of Indonesia Category:Vice presidents of Indonesia Category:1936 births Category:2019 deaths
